app_name: Red Bull TV Watch Live Events
release_note: For its 25th anniversary experience Hare Scramble in an informative and entertaining way through augmented reality. Explore a photorealistic 3 dimensional model of the Erzbergrodeo mountain zooming in and moving around the course with the touch of your fingertips. Place the mountain anywhere on a flat surface such as your living room table. Watch 360 action explanation videos of some of the hot spots of the track. Try out to tackle the most challenging areas of the race in augmented reality. Access the AR experience by tapping on the AR button located at the top left corner of the Home screen.

app_name: Red Bull TV Watch Live Events
release_note: Enjoy Red Bull Rampage like never before with an Augmented Reality experience: Explore a photorealistic 3 dimensional model of the mountain zooming in and moving around the course with the touch of your fingertips. Watch live 360 degree cameras placed in key locations around the course during the live broadcast providing you with real time unprecedented access to never before seen angles and the ability to look in any direction by simply rotating your phone. Visit multiple points of interest located across the virtual mountain that lets you access exclusive content including 360 behind the scenes footage. Don t miss a second of the action a live in app billboard will feature the livestream broadcast so when you re exploring all the cool features of the mountain you won t miss any downhill goodness. Tap on each riders name to see their run mapped to their exact line down the mountain. Access the AR experience by tapping on the AR button located at the top left corner of the Discover screen.
